    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Latex在学了在学了（</p><h3 id="A-Sum-of-Three"><a href="#A-Sum-of-Three" class="headerlink" title="A.Sum of Three"></a>A.Sum of Three</h3><p>简单观察一下不难发现对于n&#x3D;3k小于12时无解，n&#x3D;3k+1小于7无解，n&#x3D;3k+2小于8无解</p><h4 id="Code"><a href="#Code" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> LL long long</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> T;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> x;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">read</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,w=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> ch=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>||ch&gt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>) w=<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>        ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&gt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;ch&lt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        x=x*<span class="hljs-number">10</span>+ch<span class="hljs-number">-48</span>;<br>       ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x*w;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    T=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (T--) &#123;<br>        x=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (x%<span class="hljs-number">3</span>==<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (x&lt;<span class="hljs-number">12</span>) <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;NO\n&quot;</span>);<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;YES\n1 4 %d\n&quot;</span>,x<span class="hljs-number">-5</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (x%<span class="hljs-number">3</span>==<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (x&lt;<span class="hljs-number">7</span>) <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;NO\n&quot;</span>);<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;YES\n1 2 %d\n&quot;</span>,x<span class="hljs-number">-3</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (x%<span class="hljs-number">3</span>==<span class="hljs-number">2</span>)<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (x&lt;<span class="hljs-number">8</span>) <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;NO\n&quot;</span>);<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;YES\n1 2 %d\n&quot;</span>,x<span class="hljs-number">-3</span>);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="B-Fear-of-the-Dark"><a href="#B-Fear-of-the-Dark" class="headerlink" title="B.Fear of the Dark"></a>B.Fear of the Dark</h3><p>分四种情况O-A-P，O-B-P，O-A-B-P，O-B-A-P<br>取最小值即可</p><h4 id="CODE"><a href="#CODE" class="headerlink" title="CODE"></a>CODE</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> LL long long</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> T;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> xy[<span class="hljs-number">5</span>][<span class="hljs-number">3</span>];<br><span class="hljs-type">double</span> ans;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">read</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,w=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> ch=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>||ch&gt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>) w=<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>        ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&gt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;ch&lt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        x=x*<span class="hljs-number">10</span>+ch<span class="hljs-number">-48</span>;<br>       ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x*w;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">sqr</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> a*a;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">double</span> <span class="hljs-title">dis</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> a,<span class="hljs-type">int</span> b)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">sqrt</span>((<span class="hljs-type">double</span>)(<span class="hljs-built_in">sqr</span>(xy[a][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]-xy[b][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>])+<span class="hljs-built_in">sqr</span>(xy[a][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>]-xy[b][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>])));<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    T=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (T--) &#123;<br>        ans=<span class="hljs-number">1e9</span>;<br>        xy[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=xy[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        xy[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>(); xy[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>]=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>        xy[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>(); xy[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>]=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>        xy[<span class="hljs-number">3</span>][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>(); xy[<span class="hljs-number">3</span>][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>]=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>        <span class="hljs-type">double</span> t;<br>        t=<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>),<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>));<br>        ans=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(ans,t);<br>        t=<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>),<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>));<br>        ans=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(ans,t);<br>        t=<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">2</span>),<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>)/<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">3</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)));<br>        ans=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(ans,t);<br>        t=<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>),<span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">3</span>)/<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-built_in">dis</span>(<span class="hljs-number">2</span>,<span class="hljs-number">0</span>)));<br>        ans=<span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(ans,t);<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%.10lf\n&quot;</span>,ans);<br>    &#125;<br><br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="C-Decreasing-String"><a href="#C-Decreasing-String" class="headerlink" title="C.Decreasing String"></a>C.Decreasing String</h3><p>根据题意每次要删掉第一个比后面大的字符，直接单调栈维护一下就行<br>字符串单调增后从尾部继续删<br>然后算一下要输出的是删了多少次的第几个字符</p><h4 id="Code-1"><a href="#Code-1" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> LL long long</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxn = <span class="hljs-number">1e6</span> + <span class="hljs-number">5</span>;<br>LL T;<br><span class="hljs-type">char</span> ch[maxn];<br>LL v[maxn];<br>LL m,len;<br>LL cnt,head,tail;<br>LL num,l[maxn];<br><span class="hljs-function">LL <span class="hljs-title">read</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    LL x=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,w=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> ch=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>||ch&gt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>) w=<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>        ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&gt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;ch&lt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        x=x*<span class="hljs-number">10</span>+ch<span class="hljs-number">-48</span>;<br>       ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x*w;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    T=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>    l[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (T--) &#123;<br>        cnt=num=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%s&quot;</span>,&amp;ch);<br>        len=<span class="hljs-built_in">strlen</span>(ch);<br>        m=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=len;i++) v[i]=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=len;m&gt;i;i--) cnt++,m-=i;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!cnt) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%c&quot;</span>,ch[m<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=len;i++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">char</span> now=ch[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>];<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (num&amp;&amp;cnt&amp;&amp;now&lt;ch[l[num]<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]) v[l[num]]=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,num--,cnt--;<br>            l[++num]=i;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!cnt) <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (cnt) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=len;i&amp;&amp;cnt;i--)<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!v[i]) v[i]=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,cnt--;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=len;i++) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!v[i]) m--;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!m) &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%c&quot;</span>,ch[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]);<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">break</span>;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">putchar</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>);<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="D-Monocarp-and-the-Set"><a href="#D-Monocarp-and-the-Set" class="headerlink" title="D.Monocarp and the Set"></a>D.Monocarp and the Set</h3><p>第一个插入的数只可能是&gt;或者&lt;，如果s1&#x3D;?则答案为0<br>对于第i个插入的数，&lt;或者&gt;都只有一种情况，而?则可以插在非边界的任意位置，共(i-1)种可能<br>答案即为所有的(i-1)的积<br>对于后续修改只考虑修改后的贡献即可。</p><h4 id="Code-2"><a href="#Code-2" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> LL long long</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxn = <span class="hljs-number">3e5</span> + <span class="hljs-number">5</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> LL P = <span class="hljs-number">998244353</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> n,m;<br><span class="hljs-type">char</span> ch[maxn];<br>LL inv[maxn];<br>LL ans=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> len;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">read</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,w=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> ch=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>||ch&gt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>) w=<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>        ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&gt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;ch&lt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        x=x*<span class="hljs-number">10</span>+ch<span class="hljs-number">-48</span>;<br>       ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x*w;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">void</span> <span class="hljs-title">re</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    inv[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">2</span>;i&lt;=n;i++)<br>        inv[i]=(LL)(P-P/i)*inv[P%i]%P;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    n=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>(); m=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%s&quot;</span>,&amp;ch);<br>    len=<span class="hljs-built_in">strlen</span>(ch);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;len;i++)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch[i]==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;?&#x27;</span>) ans=(ans*(LL)i)%P;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;?&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0\n&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%lld\n&quot;</span>,ans);<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">re</span>();<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (m--) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> k;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">char</span> z;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">scanf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d%c%c&quot;</span>,&amp;k,&amp;z,&amp;z);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (k!=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch[k<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;?&#x27;</span>) ans=(ans*inv[k<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>])%P;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (z==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;?&#x27;</span>) ans=(ans*(LL)(k<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>))%P;<br>        &#125;<br>        ch[k<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]=z;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]!=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;?&#x27;</span>) <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%lld\n&quot;</span>,ans);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;0\n&quot;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="E-I-Wanna-be-the-Team-Leader"><a href="#E-I-Wanna-be-the-Team-Leader" class="headerlink" title="E.I Wanna be the Team Leader"></a>E.I Wanna be the Team Leader</h3><p>首先按能力值从大到小排序，因为一个任务的人数取决于能力值最低的人，那么对于一个任务分配的人一定是连续的，那么对于所有任务来说，分配的人一定是排序后的一段前缀。<br>其次注意到m&lt;&#x3D;20，考虑状压dp。<br>令f[S]表示完成的任务集合为S时分配的人数，i为接下来要完成的任务编号<br>那么f(S)&#x3D;f(S^(1&lt;&lt;(i-1)))+接下来分配给第i个任务的人数，<br>对于这一段的人数，可以通过预处理nxt(i,j)表示从第j个人开始，完成第i个任务需要分配到第几个人。<br>方程即为f(S)&#x3D;nxt(i,f(S^(1&lt;&lt;(i-1)))+1)<br>同时用lst(S)记录到达S状态最后完成的任务编号，输出答案的时候一层一层往下减</p><h4 id="Code-3"><a href="#Code-3" class="headerlink" title="Code"></a>Code</h4><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br><span class="line">76</span><br><span class="line">77</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs C++"><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">include</span><span class="hljs-string">&lt;bits/stdc++.h&gt;</span></span><br><span class="hljs-meta">#<span class="hljs-keyword">define</span> LL long long</span><br><span class="hljs-keyword">using</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> std;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxn = <span class="hljs-number">2e5</span> + <span class="hljs-number">5</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">const</span> <span class="hljs-type">int</span> maxm = <span class="hljs-number">2e1</span> + <span class="hljs-number">5</span>;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> lst[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-number">20</span>];<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> f[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;<span class="hljs-number">20</span>];<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> n,m;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">struct</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">sdd</span> &#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> c,num;<br>&#125;a[maxn];<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> v[maxn];<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> cnt;<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> nxt[maxm][maxn];<br><span class="hljs-type">int</span> ans[maxm][<span class="hljs-number">3</span>];<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">read</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>,w=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-type">char</span> ch=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&lt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>||ch&gt;<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (ch==<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span>) w=<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>        ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (ch&gt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;0&#x27;</span>&amp;&amp;ch&lt;=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;9&#x27;</span>) &#123;<br>        x=x*<span class="hljs-number">10</span>+ch<span class="hljs-number">-48</span>;<br>       ch=<span class="hljs-built_in">getchar</span>();<br>    &#125;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x*w;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">bool</span> <span class="hljs-title">cmp</span><span class="hljs-params">(sdd x,sdd y)</span> </span>&#123;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> x.c&gt;y.c;<br>&#125;<br><span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">main</span><span class="hljs-params">()</span></span><br><span class="hljs-function"></span>&#123;<br>    n=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>(); m=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=n;i++) a[i].c=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>(),a[i].num=i;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++) v[i]=<span class="hljs-built_in">read</span>();<br>    <span class="hljs-built_in">sort</span>(a+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>,a+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>+n,cmp);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++)<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j=n;j;j--) &#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!nxt[i][j]||(nxt[i][j]&gt;nxt[i][j+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]&amp;&amp;nxt[i][j+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>])) nxt[i][j]=nxt[i][j+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> x=v[i]/a[j].c+(v[i]%a[j].c!=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>);<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (j-x+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&gt;<span class="hljs-number">0</span>) nxt[i][j-x+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=j;<br>        &#125;<br>    f[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;m);i++) f[i]=<span class="hljs-number">1e9</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;m);i++) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;j&lt;=m;j++)&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (((<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;(j<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>))&amp;i)) &#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-type">int</span> llst=i^(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;(j<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>)),st=f[llst]+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (f[llst]&gt;=n) <span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span>;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (!nxt[j][st]) <span class="hljs-keyword">continue</span>;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (f[i]&gt;nxt[j][st]) f[i]=nxt[j][st],lst[i]=j;<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-type">int</span> now=(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;m)<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (f[now]&gt;n) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;NO\n&quot;</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>    &#125; <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;YES\n&quot;</span>);<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">while</span> (now) &#123;<br>        ans[lst[now]][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>]=f[now];<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> next=now^(<span class="hljs-number">1</span>&lt;&lt;(lst[now]<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>));<br>        ans[lst[now]][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]=f[next]+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        now=next;<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++) &#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>,ans[i][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>]-ans[i][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>]+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>);<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span> (<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j=ans[i][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];j&lt;=ans[i][<span class="hljs-number">2</span>];j++)<br>            <span class="hljs-built_in">printf</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&quot;%d &quot;</span>,a[j].num);<br>        <span class="hljs-built_in">putchar</span>(<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;\n&#x27;</span>);<br>    &#125;<br><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    
